sourcesContent: import mainApi from "../mainApi";    export default {        name: "Apps",        data: function () {            return {                appList: null,                dialog: false,                domains: null            }        },        methods: {            loadDomains(appName) {                mainApi().get('/apps/' + appName + '/domains', {})                    .then(response => {                        this.domains = response.data.domains;                    }).catch(e => {                    console.log(e);                })            }        },        created() {            mainApi().get('apps', {})                .then(response => {                    this.appList = response.data.apps;                }).catch(e => {                console.log(e)            });        }    }
